name: People of Crypto #003 - CZ
description:
Changpeng Zhao a.k.a CZ, is the founder of Binance and current CEO. It was founded in 2017 during the crypto boom and became the largest crypto exchange in the world by daily trading volume. 

He once worked with a subcontractor at Tokyo Stock Exchange, then founded Fusion System, a high-speed frequency trading system for brokers. Right before Binance, CZ previously worked at OKCoin as their CTO. 

But the most interesting fact is, during his teenage years, he worked at McDonald’s.

Minted on Oct,7th 2021. Will burn all remaining unsold on Oct,14st 2021
